<SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript">
    function textlimit(field, limit) {
        if (field.value.length > limit)
            field.value = field.value.substring(0, limit);
    }
</script>
<p><b><i>What you need to know before joining Axiom</i></b> :</p>
<p>Our guild is recruiting new members starting at level 35. Why this minimum 
  limit ? Because if you look at the <a href="charlist.php" target="_blank">guild 
  roster</a>, you will see that average level of members is above this number 
  (for Main chars, not counting all alts). As we want all members to be included 
  in most of the events we are planning, we prefer to ask members to at least 
  have a character in the level range above 35.</p>
<p>How to be recruited ? You can first have a look at our <a href="charter.php" target="_blank">charter</a> 
  to see the main rules. If you feel comfortable with this charter and are in 
  the right level range, you can fill the form below and send a tell to the officers 
  or leader of Axiom guild while online (see list below). If you meet recruitment 
  criteria, you'll then be invited and your data will be validated and will appear 
  on the guild roster. </p>
